##### MF3: REACTION CROSS SECTIONS                                1840 1451
                                                                  1840 1451
All the data present in the following MT-sections have been       1840 1451
calculated with TALYS, possibly normalized to experimental data.  1840 1451
If the maximal cross section in an excitation function over the   1840 1451
whole energy range does not exceed 1.e-9 b, the MT-number is not  1840 1451
included. Cross sections lower than 1.e-20 b are assumed to have  1840 1451
no physical meaning and are set to zero. All MT numbers extend up 1840 1451
to the highest incident energy.                                   1840 1451
The following reaction channels/MT numbers are generally included:1840 1451
                                                                  1840 1451
- MT1      : Total cross section                                  1840 1451
                                                                  1840 1451
Calculated with the optical model over the whole energy range,    1840 1451
or partly reproduced using experimental data.                     1840 1451
                                                                  1840 1451
- MT2      : Elastic scattering cross section                     1840 1451
                                                                  1840 1451
Obtained by subtracting the non-elastic cross section from the    1840 1451
total cross section.                                              1840 1451
                                                                  1840 1451
- MT3      : Non-elastic cross section                            1840 1451
                                                                  1840 1451
Calculated with the optical model over the whole energy range.    1840 1451
                                                                  1840 1451
- MT4      : Total inelastic cross section                        1840 1451
                                                                  1840 1451
Sum of MT=51-91.                                                  1840 1451
                                                                  1840 1451
